## CBT for OCD {.small}


::: {.cell}

:::



- Efficacy of CBT for OCD^[[Abramowitz et al. (2010)](http://dx.doi.org/10.1037/a0018260)]
  - Pre-treatment population $M = 30.25; SD = 14.89$
  - Suppose a treated individual scores $X = 15.49$

:::: {.columns}

::: {.column width="50%"}
![](media/cbt-dist.svg){.invertable}
:::

::: {.column width="50%"}
$\begin{align} z & = \dfrac{X - M}{s} \\
& = \dfrac{15.49 - 30.25}{14.89} \\
& = -0.99 \end{align}$
:::

